snippet.title: Equipmentris Patch 1.1.0 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Equipmentris is the game I originally made for #7DRL challenge. This patch introduces loads of new content such as different races and more skills and weapons. Of course also fixed the known bugs.

Play online or download at https://anttihaavikko.itch.io/equipmentris
